    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and totally ready for its next adventure with you! It\u2019s been well-loved and still runs like a total dream. Whether you need a dependable commuter or a fun car for weekend getaways, this one is a fantastic fit. Come take it for a spin, I just know you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
