    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically sound, the Vanos system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014critical for long-term chassis rigidity. It rides on a refined suspension setup with fresh bushings, ensuring the communicative steering and balanced 50/50 weight distribution remain sharp. Minor cosmetic wear consistent with age, but the drivetrain is dialed and ready for the backroads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
