    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-cared-for daily driver that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of its time on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are firm and comfortable, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine delivers consistent, smooth power, backed by a comprehensive service history that includes a recent oil change and brake inspection. The tires have significant tread remaining, ensuring a confident grip in all conditions. This car offers a reliable, refined driving experience and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without the need for immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
